'''[[Arse]] About Face''' is an [[idiom]] for something that is placed or arranged the opposite way to the way it should be.

''e.g. No wonder it doesn't look right mate, you've got the whole thing arse about face.''

The idiom is popular in the [[UK|United Kingdom]] and [[Australia]]

Examples of other idioms are:

* [[back seat driver]]
* [[kick the bucket]]